Brief description of app: This app will allow customers to place orders based on commodities chosen from the catalog. 
Customer will create account to place an order 
Admin shall confirm the account through an email confirmation 
Admin shall create credentials for customer and sends to customer through email
Customer shall not create or change credentials on their own
Customer can place orders through catalog
Admin shall have access to a web portal for administration purpose 
Customer app shall be available on the App store and Play store
Alerts shall be sent to an email when an order is placed by the customer
Orders are saved in the admin portal and in the customerâ€™s app side
Admin will upload images of commodities to be shown on the catalog
Admin will write a description passage for the image uploaded in the catalog

Will not haves:
Will not have a payment gateway, payments are done outside the app system

